<figure class="image pb-2 px-2 pt-2">
  <%= image_tag 'about.png', alt: 'Screenshots of Newsfeed' %>
</figure>
<section class="section content pt-3">
  <h1 class="title">
    About Newsfeed
  </h1>
  <p>
    Newsfeed is a Really Simple Newsreader for RSS (and ATOM and all that).
  </p>
  <p>
    After years on social media, Feedly, and other excellent but complicated news aggregators a return to flowing over news and not worrying too much is needed.
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Readable, scannable, ignorable</li>
    <li>Simple organisation</li>
    <li>Recallable</li>
    <li>Reverse chronological with transparent cleanup</li>
    <Li>Fast, because it's simple</li>
    <li>Dozens, not hundreds, of feeds</li>
    <li>Only rough timestamps</li>
    <li>No unread counts</li>
    <li>Not real time</li>
  </ul>
  <p>
    Built for and by <a href="https://paulmwatson.com">Paul Watson</a> but if you like it then great, <%= link_to 'sign up', :new_user_registration %>.
  </p>
</section>